<h2 id="org1bb47f6">Deletig and Disabling Linux</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org1bb47f6">
<p>
type -a userdel    # not found
which userdel      # no userdel in 
</p>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li>options : userdel cmd is outside the path of shell</li>
